; 46:6; 67:19; 72:17; 79(80):2; 80:1; 85(86):12; 103(104):30; 107:20; 108:3; 117(118):26-7; 118(119):89; Prov 3:12; Lam 3:4; 30:30; Is 7:14a; 7:14b; 7:14; 9:6; 21:2; 21:7; 21:9; 35:3-4; 35:4-6; 35:5-6; 40:8; 50:6; 53:5; 53:8; 63:9; 64:1;  Dan 2:32-33; 2:34-35; 7:5-6; 7:13-14; 9:25; 9:26; Zech 9:9; 13:6-7; Matt 3:11; 6:9; 11:13; 28:19; 27:51-52; Mk 13:25; Lk 1:13-17; 3:16; Jn 1:1; 1:4; 1:27; 1:29; 10:17-18; 14:26; 15:26; 16:13-15; 16:14; 17:5; 16:20; Acts 2:1-4; 1 Cor 2:10; 2 Cor 4:6.</note></biblStruct><bibl type="formatted" subtype="https://www.zotero.org/styles/chicago-note-bibliography-16th-edition">
